INSERT INTO `tbl_deleted_article` VALUES ('1000031625817427293', 'Required request part \'editormd-image-file\' is not present', 100003, 'Required request part ‘editormd-image-file’ is not present我是用的SSM框架搭建的博客系统，使用editormd进行图片上传的时候遇到了问题： 后端报错Required request part \'editormd-image-file\' i......', 1, 1, '2021-07-08 00:00:00', '2021-07-08 00:00:00', '# Required request part \'editormd-image-file\' is not present\\n\\n我是用的SSM框架搭建的博客系统，使用editormd进行图片上传的时候遇到了问题：\\n\\n后端报错`Required request part \'editormd-image-file\' is not present`\\n\\n前端报错`cannot parse json` // 具体错误记不清了，反正就是不能把一个对象转换为json格式\\n\\n废话不多说，直接上解决方案。\\n\\nSpringMVC处理MultipartFile的时候要进行两个地方的配置：\\n\\nSpringMVC配置文件中添加\\n\\n```xml\\n<!--dispatcherServlet-servlet.xml -->\\n\\n<bean id=\"multipartResolver\" class=\"org.springframework.web.multipart.commons.CommonsMultipartResolver\">\\n    <!-- 文件上传的最大值-->\\n    <property name=\"maxUploadSize\" value=\"10485760\"></property>\\n    <!-- 文件上传时写入内存的最大值，默认为10240 -->\\n    <property name=\"maxInMemorySize\" value=\"4096\"></property>\\n    <!-- 默认编码 -->\\n    <property name=\"defaultEncoding\" value=\"UTF-8\"></property>\\n</bean>\\n```\\n\\n项目中引入依赖\\n\\n```xml\\n<!--pom.xml-->\\n	<dependency>\\n      <groupId>commons-fileupload</groupId>\\n      <artifactId>commons-fileupload</artifactId>\\n      <version>1.2.2</version>\\n    </dependency>\\n    <dependency>\\n      <groupId>commons-io</groupId>\\n      <artifactId>commons-io</artifactId>\\n      <version>2.0.1</version>\\n    </dependency>\\n```\\n\\n\\n\\n解决了这两个问题之后就好了。', '<div class=\"markdown-body editormd-preview-container\" previewcontainer=\"true\" style=\"padding: 20px;\"><h1 id=\"h1-required-request-part-editormd-image-file-is-not-present\"><a name=\"Required request part ‘editormd-image-file’ is not present\" class=\"reference-link\"></a><span class=\"header-link octicon octicon-link\"></span>Required request part ‘editormd-image-file’ is not present</h1><p>我是用的SSM框架搭建的博客系统，使用editormd进行图片上传的时候遇到了问题：</p>\n<p>后端报错<code>Required request part \'editormd-image-file\' is not present</code></p>\n<p>前端报错<code>cannot parse json</code> // 具体错误记不清了，反正就是不能把一个对象转换为json格式</p>\n<p>废话不多说，直接上解决方案。</p>\n<p>SpringMVC处理MultipartFile的时候要进行两个地方的配置：</p>\n<p>SpringMVC配置文件中添加</p>\n<pre class=\"prettyprint linenums prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><ol class=\"linenums\"><li class=\"L0\"><code class=\"lang-xml\"><span class=\"com\">&lt;!--dispatcherServlet-servlet.xml --&gt;</span></code></li><li class=\"L1\"><code class=\"lang-xml\"></code></li><li class=\"L2\"><code class=\"lang-xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;bean</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">id</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"multipartResolver\"</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">class</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"org.springframework.web.multipart.commons.CommonsMultipartResolver\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;</span></code></li><li class=\"L3\"><code class=\"lang-xml\"><span class=\"pln\">    </span><span class=\"com\">&lt;!-- 文件上传的最大值--&gt;</span></code></li><li class=\"L4\"><code class=\"lang-xml\"><span class=\"pln\">    </span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;property</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">name</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"maxUploadSize\"</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">value</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"10485760\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;&lt;/property&gt;</span></code></li><li class=\"L5\"><code class=\"lang-xml\"><span class=\"pln\">    </span><span class=\"com\">&lt;!-- 文件上传时写入内存的最大值，默认为10240 --&gt;</span></code></li><li class=\"L6\"><code class=\"lang-xml\"><span class=\"pln\">    </span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;property</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">name</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"maxInMemorySize\"</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">value</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"4096\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;&lt;/property&gt;</span></code></li><li class=\"L7\"><code class=\"lang-xml\"><span class=\"pln\">    </span><span class=\"com\">&lt;!-- 默认编码 --&gt;</span></code></li><li class=\"L8\"><code class=\"lang-xml\"><span class=\"pln\">    </span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;property</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">name</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"defaultEncoding\"</span><span class=\"pln\"> </span><span class=\"atn\">value</span><span class=\"pun\">=</span><span class=\"atv\">\"UTF-8\"</span><span class=\"tag\">&gt;&lt;/property&gt;</span></code></li><li class=\"L9\"><code class=\"lang-xml\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/bean&gt;</span></code></li></ol></pre>\n<p>项目中引入依赖</p>\n<pre class=\"prettyprint linenums prettyprinted\" style=\"\"><ol class=\"linenums\"><li class=\"L0\"><code class=\"lang-xml\"><span class=\"com\">&lt;!--pom.xml--&gt;</span></code></li><li class=\"L1\"><code class=\"lang-xml\"><span class=\"pln\">    </span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;dependency&gt;</span></code></li><li class=\"L2\"><code class=\"lang-xml\"><span class=\"pln\">      </span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;groupId&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">commons-fileupload</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/groupId&gt;</span></code></li><li class=\"L3\"><code class=\"lang-xml\"><span class=\"pln\">      </span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;artifactId&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">commons-fileupload</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/artifactId&gt;</span></code></li><li class=\"L4\"><code class=\"lang-xml\"><span class=\"pln\">      </span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;version&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">1.2.2</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/version&gt;</span></code></li><li class=\"L5\"><code class=\"lang-xml\"><span class=\"pln\">    </span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/dependency&gt;</span></code></li><li class=\"L6\"><code class=\"lang-xml\"><span class=\"pln\">    </span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;dependency&gt;</span></code></li><li class=\"L7\"><code class=\"lang-xml\"><span class=\"pln\">      </span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;groupId&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">commons-io</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/groupId&gt;</span></code></li><li class=\"L8\"><code class=\"lang-xml\"><span class=\"pln\">      </span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;artifactId&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">commons-io</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/artifactId&gt;</span></code></li><li class=\"L9\"><code class=\"lang-xml\"><span class=\"pln\">      </span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;version&gt;</span><span class=\"pln\">2.0.1</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/version&gt;</span></code></li><li class=\"L0\"><code class=\"lang-xml\"><span class=\"pln\">    </span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/dependency&gt;</span></code></li></ol></pre>\n<p>解决了这两个问题之后就好了。</p>\n</div>');
